      "content": "it's not even about worth. it's just that the half of me that made sense is gone. i look at my life and i don't see a person anymore, just an empty shell. it feels like i'm just lingering, like i'm stuck in this waiting room between life and death. honestly, sometimes it feels more natural to just... not be here. to just let the silence finally win.",
